{"tid":1305436,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"法國擬徵數碼服務稅 美國宣布按301條款啟動調查","createTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:45.000Z","uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"bedbc1d017086241d993d6e420e978c45b2f81c8","tid":1305436,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:10.000Z","msg":"法國擬徵數碼服務稅 美國宣布按301條款啟動調查<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E5%BE%B5%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E7%A8%85-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%8C%89301%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-223128892.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E6%25B3%2595%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%25AC%25E5%25BE%25B5%25E6%2595%25B8%25E7%25A2%25BC%25E6%259C%258D%25E5%258B%2599%25E7%25A8%2585-%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E5%25AE%25A3%25E5%25B8%2583%25E6%258C%2589301%25E6%25A2%259D%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E5%2595%259F%25E5%258B%2595%25E8%25AA%25BF%25E6%259F%25A5-223128892.html&d=GTvhkYpGRy3WajvnblfJnc04bh6pArHnk2fwDmvpgUU%3D&h=7b4f5680\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E6%B3%95%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%AC%E5%BE%B5%E6%95%B8%E7%A2%BC%E6%9C%8D%E5%8B%99%E7%A8%85-%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%A3%E5%B8%83%E6%8C%89301%E6%A2%9D%E6%AC%BE%E5%95%9F%E5%8B%95%E8%AA%BF%E6%9F%A5-223128892.html</a><br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表處表示，將會根據《1974年貿易法》第301條款，啟動調查法國計劃向數碼服務徵稅。<br />\n<br />\n美國貿易代表萊特希澤在聲明表示，美國非常關注法國國會即將通過向數碼服務徵稅，明顯是不公平地針對美國公司。<br />\n<br />\n法國計劃向提供數碼服務的公司，按年度收入3%徵收稅項。法國認為，只有大型科技公司會受影響。外界相信，徵稅極可能影響美國跨國數碼企業，包括谷歌、亞馬遜及Facebook等。<br />\n<br />\n由於啟動301條款，涉及不公平貿易行為，可能會引致美國向法國進口貨開徵關稅。"},{"pid":"043d87e08f4da91b9d12dd472bd2968092efcac7","tid":1305436,"uid":25831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-11T00:34:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}